<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idf6a7b21f-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5" identifier="/us/usc/t46/s31308"><num value="31308">§ 31308.</num><heading> Secretary of Commerce or Transportation as mortgagee</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary of Commerce or Transportation, as a mortgagee under this chapter, may foreclose on a lien arising from a right established under a mortgage under chapter 537 of this title, subject to <ref href="/us/usc/t11/s362/b">section 362(b) of title 11</ref>.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idf6a7b220-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5">(<ref href="/us/pl/100/710/tI/s102/c">Pub. L. 100–710, title I, § 102(c)</ref>, <date date="1988-11-23">Nov. 23, 1988</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/102/4741">102 Stat. 4741</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/101/595/tVI/s603/13">Pub. L. 101–595, title VI, § 603(13)</ref>, <date date="1990-11-16">Nov. 16, 1990</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/104/2993">104 Stat. 2993</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/109/304/s15/28">Pub. L. 109–304, § 15(28)</ref>, <date date="2006-10-06">Oct. 6, 2006</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/120/1704">120 Stat. 1704</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/111/281/tIX/s913/b">Pub. L. 111–281, title IX, § 913(b)</ref>, <date date="2010-10-15">Oct. 15, 2010</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/124/3017">124 Stat. 3017</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
